                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Hay</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Bowen</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1902-12-27">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 27, 1902</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Hay communicates to Mr. Bowen the German<note n="a" xml:id="d829fna">Printed
                        under Germany, <ref target="#pg_427">page 427</ref>.</note> and British<note
                        n="b" xml:id="d829fnb">Printed under Great Britain, <ref target="#pg_461"
                            >page 461</ref>.</note> propositions in regard to preliminary conditions
                    of arbitration.)</p>
            </div>
